From: Aurabindo Pillai <mail@aurabindo.in>
Date: Wed, 8 Apr 2020 21:28:13 -0400
Subject: drm/amd/amdgpu: add prefix for pr_* prints
Git-commit: d57229b1da7204dc0ec663478bc36c8fcf0314d0
Patch-mainline: v5.8-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-12680, jsc#SLE-12880, jsc#SLE-12882, jsc#SLE-12883, jsc#SLE-13496, jsc#SLE-15322

amdgpu uses lots of pr_* calls for printing error messages.
With this prefix, errors shall be more obvious to the end
use regarding its origin, and may help debugging.

Prefix format:

[xxx.xxxxx] amdgpu: ...

Signed-off-by: Aurabindo Pillai <mail@aurabindo.in>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu.h | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu.h b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu.h
index cc41fd12a0a8..05ba12300703 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu.h
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu.h
@@ -28,6 +28,12 @@
 #ifndef __AMDGPU_H__
 #define __AMDGPU_H__
 
+#ifdef pr_fmt
+#undef pr_fmt
+#endif
+
+#define pr_fmt(fmt) "amdgpu: " fmt
+
 #include "amdgpu_ctx.h"
 
 #include <linux/atomic.h>
